column2:
"You were amazing again!
I learned something!
Anything can be experience!"

"Actually, there was a second there when I was
sure you were history, but you just kept going!
You really showed me some sick moves today!"

"Still, I'll probably run away my first time.
But I guess I can cross that bridge when I get to it.
Thanks again, friend!"

"今回もスゴかったなぁー！
勉強になった！
やっぱ何事も経験だな！"

"実際ヒヤッとする瞬間もあったけど
オレはもちろん信じてたぜ！
いい手本を見せてもらったよ。"

"でもやっぱりオレは逃げるかなぁ……
まあ、そのときになったら考えよう。
ありがとな！"
